column3: Senior reserves played significant amount of time (it's senior day)
Keeper came out nicely on breakaway and prevented goal
Skill level is low, defensive shape in the back 4 is not very disciplined, and their attack primarily consists of playing long balls which they don't do with much accuracy
Very nice attacking play in the midfield
Nice follow up to score goal
Play was getting very direct and sloppy toward the end with little build up through midfield
Defense needs to handle balls in the air better (when to head, take down on chest, dribble quickly into space)
